    <middle>
        <section title="Introduction">
            <t>
                Large BGP Communities <xref target="I-D.ietf-idr-large-community"/> provide
                a mechanism to signal opaque information between Autonomous
                Systems.

            </t>
            <t>
                This document presents a set of examples on how the Large Community
                standard could be implemented by an operator to achieve various
                goals. It should however be noted that the Large Community standard
                is opaque, any recommendations made in this document may be ignored
                by the operator.
            </t>
        </section>

